<HEADLINE> Fire Breaks Out in Central Algiers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, February 27 (Xinhua) -- A big fire engulfed a hotel and
gutted a cinema in the center of the Algerian capital of Algiers
at 15:45 local time (1445 GMT) today, according to reports
reaching here.
</P>
