police vehicles surrounded the hotel, while police sealed off the
district where the hotel was located.
</P>
<P>
The Algerian capital has been hit by a wave of bombing attacks
and assassinations since the Muslim fasting month of Ramadan in
early January, perpetrated by the country's Islamic militants
engaging in a war with the military-backed government since 1991.
</P>
