<HEADLINE> 2 Killed in Avalanche in Turkey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, February 27 (Xinhua) -- Two people were killed and one
injured today in an avalanche in southeastern Turkey, the
semi-official Anatolia News Agency reported this evening.
</P>
<P>
The agency said that the two, while going hunting, came across
the avalanche and were killed.
</P>
<P>
