project in east Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
At a press conference in his office, the foreign minister
warned that the Israeli government's decision to build more
Jewish settlements in Jerusalem will "once again ruin the peace
process" in the Middle East.
</P>
<P>
Ignoring the prospect of drawing violent reactions of
Palestinians and the Arab, the right-wing Israeli government
gave Wednesday the go-ahead for building thousands of Jewish
homes in east Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
