<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-28 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Hu Jintao on Deng Theory and CPPCC Work </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 28 (Xinhua)-- A top Chinese Communist Party
(CPC) official called here today for holding high the great banner
of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics and pushing forward the great cause of socialist
reform, and opening-up and modernization initiated by Deng.
</P>
<P>
Hu Jintao, a member of the Standing Committee of the Political
Bureau of the CPC Central Committee, made the call at a group
discussion with members of the National Committee of the Chinese
People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) who are here
attending the committee's annual session.
</P>
<P>
He said, "To accomplish this historic task, we must arm our
minds more conscientiously with Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory and
adhere to the basic line of the Party unswervingly under any
conditions.
</P>
<P>
"It also requires us to unite more closely around the Party
Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core, strengthen and
improve Party leadership, keep consolidating and improving
party building, further enhance the level of administration and
leadership."
</P>
<P>
In the meantime, he said, it is necessary for people of
different ethnic groups across the country to unite as one, work
with one heart and one mind, pool their collective wisdom and
strength, and bring such wisdom and strength into full play.
</P>
<P>
Attending the discussion were CPPCC National committee members
from the Youth League, All-China Youth Federation, All-China
Federation of Taiwan Compatriots, All-China Federation of Returned
Overseas Chinese, and the CPPCC National Committee social welfare
group.
</P>
<P>
Hu said that people's organizations they belong to are important
channels for the Party and the government to contact the masses
and overseas compatriots.
</P>
<P>
He expressed high appreciation for these organizations which he
said have united and exerted a positive influence on people they
have contacts with and played an indispensable role in pushing
forward reform, opening up and modernization in China as well as
the cause of reunification and re-invigoration of the country.
</P>
<P>
Hu said CPPCC National Committee members, as representatives of
various social circles, should correctly reflect the views of the
public and offer more advices and suggestions for the Party and the
government.
</P>
<P>
Members should also play a good role in bridging different
ideas, dissolving contradictions, and stimulating and protecting
initiatives of people in all fields, in order to maintain a close
unity of the people around the Party and the government, he said.
</P>
<P>
Hu called on members of the CPPCC National Committee to further
improve their work this year in accordance with plans of the
central authorities, hold even higher the great banner of Deng
Xiaoping's theory on building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, follow the correct path Deng Xiaoping pointed out
for CPPCC work in the new period, and make greater contributions to
the modernization drive, reunification and rejuvenation of China.
</P>
<P>
Other participants of the group discussion expressed views or
raised suggestions on studying Deng Xiaoping's theory on united
front work, strengthening education and scientific research, and
enriching socialist literature and arts, among others. 
</P>
</TEXT>
