<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, February 28 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading French newspapers today:
</P>
<P>
Liberation:
</P>
<P>
-- The United Nations Secretary General Kofi Annan has put the
improvement of relations with the United States as one of his
priorities, in order to end a state of quasi-cold war between
Washington and the United Nations that was seen in the latter half
of the mandate of Boutros Boutros-Ghali.
</P>
