<HEADLINE> Xinhua Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 28 (Xinhua) -- Today's Xinhua A stock index
gained 2.37 points to close at 144.25, while the Xinhua B stock
index increased 0.66 points to finish at 78.79.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua stock index is China's first national unitary stock
exponent, which is jointly designed and issued by the Economic
Information Department of Xinhua News Agency and Beijing
University.  
