occupation forces and Hezbollah guerrillas traded violent
artillery fires in south Lebanon this morning.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian-backed Shiite group spearheads a guerrilla warfare
to oust Israel out of the 1,100-square-kilometer buffer strip
the Jewish state established in 1985. 
