will amount to 300,000-350,000 hectares.The government had
encouraged small plant owners to grow two to five hectares each,
the report said.
</P>
<P>
The World Bank and the French Development Fund has decided to
provide 120 million U.S. dollars in soft loans to 50,000 poor
households in Dac Lac Province, in central Vietnam, to plant
50,000-60,000 hectares of rubber trees between 1998-2005. 
