anti-government agitation in district headquarters.
</P>
<P>
The announcement was made by BNP Secretary General Abdul Mannan
Bhuiyan on Thursday, a day after BNP chairperson Khaleda Zia had
threatened to launch a movement aiming to dislodge the
eight-month-old government.
</P>
<P>
