<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Pakistani Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, February 28 (Xinhua) -- The following are the major
news items in leading Pakistani English newspapers today.
</P>
<P>
The News
</P>
<P>
-- Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif Thursday offered
foreign secretary level talks to his Indian counterpart to prepare
ground for meaningful discussion at a summit dialogue as early as
possible.
</P>
<P>
