MOSCOW, February 27 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin
and U.S. President Bill Clinton will discuss the proposed eastward
expansion of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) at
their summit in Helsinki next month.
</P>
<P>
