The Russian and American delegations preparing for the summit
have winded up their two-day talks about the agenda, the press
office said.
</P>
<P>
Russia strongly opposes the enlargement of the the U.S.-led
NATO military alliance to include former Warsaw Bloc countries
in eastern Europe. 
